No. 11-350. NATSO, Inc., et al., Petitioners v. 3 Girls Enterprises, Inc., et al. 565 U.S. 1147, 132 S. Ct. 1004,

181 L. Ed. 2d 790,

2012 U.S. LEXIS 436. January 9, 2012.

Motion of Rutherford Institute for leave to file a brief as amicus curiae granted. Petition for writ of certio-rari to the United States Court of Appeals for the Tenth Circuit denied.

Same case below, 641 F.3d 470.
